Author: sharpshoot
Content:
Buxfer are from India. I think they were on student visas initially but then switched to work visas.

YC's philosophy (from talking to everyone involved) seems to be if you good enough regardless of where you are apply. Visa complications are obviously a pain but if your get in you get in.
